{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a2d4db0f87","title":"转发川西军区清匯报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"88d080abbd","index":0,"year":1951,"month":2,"day":25,"articleId":"a2d4db0f87"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"512e8eb869","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a2d4db0f87","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东为转发中国人民解放军川西军区清报告写的批语。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c65888bcf2","type":"title","text":"转发川西军区清亚报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a2d4db0f87"},{"id":"512e8eb869","type":"paragraph","text":"华东、中南、西北、华北各大军区及中央局：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a2d4db0f87"},{"id":"14ef06eb54","type":"paragraph","text":"下面是川西军区的清能报告，发给你们参考。西南的经验是县区乡均建立有党外民主人士参加的清能委员会，保有清能小组，区有捕提队，此外尚有情报站与检查站的组织。再则清必须与反霸、减租、退押或土改相结合进去，必须系掉首、惯与恶霸并必须由党委统一领导，全力以赴，才能发动群众，根绝码。以上经验请加注意，凡你区尚有能褐地区，请指导当地同志研究这些经验。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a2d4db0f87"},{"id":"7326a9193e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a2d4db0f87"},{"id":"664e74dfb9","type":"paragraph","text":"二月二十五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a2d4db0f87"}],"page":{"id":"6683e44c2d","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"a2d4db0f87","start":138,"end":138}}}},"__N_SSG":true}